Zippy:

fluttering bunting
virtuosic opacity  (relentless, ruthless)
Too fast to sink, too big to die,
Too much self-destruction.
Bubble and crash, bubble and crash.
Corporate copyright, cultural genocide.
There must be generations of fossick and hoard, tinker and trade
Whole generations of fossick and hoard, tinker and trade

By beauty of sinew and muscle, heart and lung, spine and brain
I thought she was Lulu deLight,
skintight dayglo hotpants, and a repetoire of flirty pouts.
utterly gruntled
by competitive stimulation

a hippie kid
grope and grovel, mope and mumble
Too much recreation...
misfit mystic
mystic misfit
demoded as a multi-function polis, and consistently losing at musical chairs
Utter dark words, verging on prophecy
Too much self-destruction


