This is iteration, stripped of any Long Vowels.
The Simplicity of the consonant and Shortness of the vowel are more important.
Except the Last Syllable in a phrase can be Long...
Also the First Consonant in a phrase can be a Fricative...
In the interests of Simple Consonants, words beginning with Vowels are useful

